quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,Popol Al-Hijr disbelieved messengers
  15,81,Ni don them our revelations ili disregarded them
  15,82,Ili uz carve secure hejm mont
  15,83,disaster hit them en des maten
  15,84,ki ili hoarded ne help them
  15,85,Ni ne kre heavens ter cxio them specif purpose end mond ven tial trakt them benign neglect
  15,86,Your Lord est Creator Omniscient
  15,87,Ni don vi 7 par great Quran
  15,88,Est jxaluz de ki ni bestowed ali (messengers) ne saddened disbelievers) lower your wing believers
  15,89,Proklam mi est manifest warner
  15,90,Ni deal kun dividers
  15,91,Ili akcept Quran nur partially
  15,92,Per your Lord ni question them all
  15,93,Pri cxio ili done
  15,94,Do port mend don al vi disregard idol worshipers
  15,95,Ni sxpar vi mockers
  15,96,who set another di DI! Ili do gxi surely trov out
  15,97,Ni kon plen put ke vi annoyed their utterances
  15,98,Vi kant lauxd your Lord est prostrators
  15,99,worship your Lord en ord al ating certainty